WEBVTT

00:01.760 --> 00:03.486
- ♪ Hey, here comes Sunny
keeping it fun ♪

00:03.555 --> 00:05.074
♪ Never says never,
never gives up ♪

00:05.143 --> 00:07.352
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:07.421 --> 00:08.905
♪ Hey ♪

00:08.974 --> 00:10.734
♪ Gear up and go
in the Glam Van ♪

00:10.803 --> 00:12.529
♪ Hair styling
with her best friends ♪

00:12.598 --> 00:14.945
♪ It's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:15.015 --> 00:17.879
♪ Oh, it's a Sunny Day ♪

00:17.948 --> 00:20.261
♪ She'll put a smile
on your face ♪

00:20.330 --> 00:21.918
- Whoo-hoo!

00:21.987 --> 00:26.681
- ♪ Sunny is shining
all the way ♪

00:26.750 --> 00:29.650
♪ Yeah, she's Sunny,
yeah, she's Sunny ♪

00:29.719 --> 00:32.101
♪ Having a sunny, sunny day ♪

00:32.170 --> 00:33.378
- Hoo-hoo!

00:38.797 --> 00:44.527
- "Lacey's Salon."

00:44.596 --> 00:45.804
- Ready...

00:45.873 --> 00:46.770
Set...

00:46.839 --> 00:48.358
Throw!

00:50.222 --> 00:51.775
- Yeah!
- Go Sunny!

00:51.844 --> 00:55.469
- No reason why organizing
wigs can't be fun, right?

00:57.367 --> 00:59.887
- A perfect score!
Nice throwing!

00:59.956 --> 01:01.958
- Rox, you gotta come see this!

01:02.027 --> 01:04.064
- Be right down!

01:06.445 --> 01:10.000
Hey, something's wrong
with this.

01:10.070 --> 01:12.313
Ah! Look out below!

01:12.382 --> 01:13.694
- Ah!

01:13.763 --> 01:16.145
Thanks, Doodle.
That was close!

01:16.214 --> 01:20.804
Rox! Might be a good time
to turn off that faucet!

01:20.873 --> 01:25.740
- If I could, I would,
but I can't! Oh no!

01:25.809 --> 01:28.985
- I'm coming up!
- Wait for me!

01:29.054 --> 01:32.195
- Stand back, Rox. I'll help.

01:34.232 --> 01:35.233
- Ah!

01:35.302 --> 01:36.993
- My hair's not that bad.

01:37.062 --> 01:39.547
It just needs a little trim.

01:39.616 --> 01:42.067
[pipes clattering]

01:42.136 --> 01:44.380
- Oh no!

01:44.449 --> 01:48.246
- Where'd everybody go?

01:48.315 --> 01:49.419
- Hey!

01:49.488 --> 01:51.352
- Why is everyone so upset?

01:51.421 --> 01:53.251
It's just a little water!

01:53.320 --> 01:54.769
Come on.

01:57.600 --> 02:00.016
- Oh no! We gotta do something!

02:00.085 --> 02:03.606
Or our walk-in salon
will be a swim-up salon!

02:03.675 --> 02:06.022
- Here, give me that.

02:08.507 --> 02:09.715
- Oh!

02:09.784 --> 02:11.269
- How did you do that?

02:11.338 --> 02:12.649
- Just turned off
the water main.

02:12.718 --> 02:15.411
- The water main?
- Great thinking, Lacey!

02:15.480 --> 02:17.896
- Not really. That's just how
you do it.

02:17.965 --> 02:20.070
But thanks, I guess.

02:20.140 --> 02:21.969
Here's what caused your leak.

02:22.038 --> 02:23.384
It's a rusty washer.

02:23.453 --> 02:25.145
I can replace it.

02:25.214 --> 02:28.078
- Lacey, how do you know how to
fix things like that?

02:28.148 --> 02:30.564
- How do you not know?

02:30.633 --> 02:32.876
- She's always fixing things.

02:32.945 --> 02:35.016
She unclogged
the bathtub drain,

02:35.085 --> 02:36.501
replaced our windows.

02:36.570 --> 02:39.435
She even changed the tire
on her motorcycle.

02:39.504 --> 02:41.402
- Wow, that's impressive!

02:41.471 --> 02:44.819
- Will someone hand me that
wrench, please?

02:44.888 --> 02:46.649
- That's a hammer.

02:48.927 --> 02:52.413
- So that's a hammer!
Huh! Well, what do you know?

02:55.002 --> 02:57.177
- There we go Lacey, all done!

02:57.246 --> 02:58.385
[doorbell rings]

02:58.454 --> 02:59.765
- Sunny, I had to tell you!

02:59.834 --> 03:01.491
Everyone loves my new
hairstyle!

03:01.560 --> 03:04.356
You're the most talented
hairstylist ever!

03:04.425 --> 03:06.151
- [giggles] Thanks!

03:06.220 --> 03:09.154
- Could I--would you
take a picture with me

03:09.223 --> 03:10.638
and my new hair?

03:10.707 --> 03:12.675
- Um...sure!

03:12.744 --> 03:16.679
- Whoa, Sunny! That makes you
like a rock star!

03:16.748 --> 03:18.991
Cool! Can I have your
autograph?

03:19.060 --> 03:22.857
- KC, what's so special about
being a hairstylist anyway?

03:22.926 --> 03:24.411
It can't be that hard!

03:24.480 --> 03:27.172
I could be a great hairstylist,

03:27.241 --> 03:28.587
if I wanted to.

03:28.656 --> 03:30.762
- Sorry about that, Lacey.

03:30.831 --> 03:32.867
- Your hair looks wonderful,
Lacey!

03:32.936 --> 03:34.662
Sunny, you did an amazing job!

03:34.731 --> 03:37.458
- Well, my hair's doing
some of the work.

03:37.527 --> 03:40.496
- Oh, you should take home a
bottle of Sunny's Glam Shampoo!

03:40.565 --> 03:42.981
It'll help keep your hair
under control.

03:43.050 --> 03:46.295
- Hmm...I'll think about it.

03:46.364 --> 03:48.849
- Whoa! Oh!

03:48.918 --> 03:50.747
- Watch it!
- Sorry!

03:50.816 --> 03:53.094
- Timmy! What's all this?

03:53.163 --> 03:56.028
- It's for my client.
Well, your client.

03:56.097 --> 03:58.410
The most amazing client ever!

03:58.479 --> 03:59.446
Dame--

03:59.515 --> 04:01.482
- ♪ La la la la ♪

04:01.551 --> 04:04.382
[Doodle howls]

04:04.451 --> 04:05.659
- It can't be!

04:05.728 --> 04:09.041
It is! I know that voice
anywhere!

04:09.110 --> 04:10.491
- ♪ La la la la la ♪

04:10.560 --> 04:13.908
- Presenting Dame Tralada!

04:13.977 --> 04:15.427
- Dame What-o-what?

04:15.496 --> 04:17.222
- Dame Tralada!

04:17.291 --> 04:19.604
Only the best opera
singer ever!

04:19.673 --> 04:22.572
- Oof!

04:22.641 --> 04:27.301
What can I say?
♪ It is true ♪

04:27.370 --> 04:30.511
- Dame Tralada, it's an honor
to have you in our salon.

04:30.580 --> 04:34.204
- I know. And now I must rest
my voice.

04:37.035 --> 04:38.312
- Ah!

04:38.381 --> 04:41.453
The Dame wants me to ask
if you'll style her hair

04:41.522 --> 04:43.006
for her performance tonight.

04:43.075 --> 04:45.733
- A performance?
Here in Friendly Falls?

04:45.802 --> 04:47.148
What? Where? When?

04:47.217 --> 04:49.081
- The Dame is singing
the lead in an opera

04:49.150 --> 04:51.498
called "The Rinse Cycle!"

04:51.567 --> 04:56.226
- "The Rinse Cycle?" That's my
most favorite opera ever!

04:56.296 --> 04:58.712
You must be playing Hildegard.

04:58.781 --> 05:00.438
- What's a Hildegard?

05:00.507 --> 05:02.854
- No idea.

05:05.339 --> 05:07.859
- Yep! That's exactly the style
she needs!

05:07.928 --> 05:11.759
I told the Dame you're the best
hairstylist in town, Sunny.

05:11.828 --> 05:13.382
- She sure is!
- The very best!

05:13.451 --> 05:15.763
- "Most talented?"
"Best in town?"

05:15.832 --> 05:19.698
"Rock star?" Why does everyone
think Sunny's so special?

05:19.767 --> 05:21.286
- Wh--

05:21.355 --> 05:24.289
- Ah! I will speak now!

05:24.358 --> 05:25.497
- Zip!

05:25.566 --> 05:28.258
- My hair needs to be perfect.

05:28.328 --> 05:30.985
If I'm not in character,
I cannot sing.

05:31.054 --> 05:32.539
And if I cannot sing,

05:32.608 --> 05:34.851
♪ there is no opera ♪

05:34.920 --> 05:36.336
[Doodle howls]

05:36.405 --> 05:38.096
- I'd be happy to help.

05:38.165 --> 05:39.822
We can start now if you like.

05:39.891 --> 05:40.995
- ♪ No ♪

05:41.064 --> 05:42.065
Later.

05:42.134 --> 05:44.171
Now I must have my rest.

05:44.240 --> 05:47.208
If I don't have my rest,
I cannot sing.

05:47.277 --> 05:48.865
And if I cannot sing,

05:48.934 --> 05:49.901
♪ there's ♪

05:49.970 --> 05:52.800
- ♪ No opera ♪

05:52.869 --> 05:53.836
We got that.

05:53.905 --> 05:55.838
- Oh, I have an idea.

05:55.907 --> 05:57.978
We can pick you up at your
hotel,

05:58.047 --> 06:00.049
get you styled in the Glam Van,

06:00.118 --> 06:02.120
and then drive you straight
to the opera.

06:02.189 --> 06:05.848
- Glam Van? It sounds
glamorous.

06:05.917 --> 06:07.470
♪ Like me ♪

06:07.539 --> 06:10.128
Very well, I shall see you
later at the hotel.

06:10.197 --> 06:13.545
♪ Timothy, we must go ♪

06:13.614 --> 06:17.687
- Wow, her voice sure packs
a wallop, doesn't it?

06:17.756 --> 06:19.655
[mumbling]

06:19.724 --> 06:20.794
See you later!

06:20.863 --> 06:21.898
- Have a sunny day!

06:21.967 --> 06:23.452
- Bye!
- Bye-bye!

06:23.521 --> 06:26.351
- I know I can be as good
a hairstylist as Sunny.

06:26.420 --> 06:29.147
Better! I'm good
at fixing things, right?

06:29.216 --> 06:31.943
I fixed the sink,
I can fix hair too.

06:32.012 --> 06:34.221
- I don't know, Lacey.

06:34.290 --> 06:36.913
Sunny's been doing this
a long time, and--

06:36.982 --> 06:39.019
- I'm gonna prove it!

06:39.088 --> 06:42.609
We're gonna open our own salon!

06:42.678 --> 06:45.163
Then everyone will see
that I'm the best hairstylist

06:45.232 --> 06:48.028
and they'll treat me like
a rock star too!

06:48.097 --> 06:51.721
And our first customer will be
Dame Tra-ba-da-da.

06:51.790 --> 06:53.240
- It's Tralada.

06:53.309 --> 06:56.450
- I'll just need a comb,
scissors...

06:56.519 --> 06:58.141
Ah!

06:58.210 --> 06:59.557
That should do it.

06:59.626 --> 07:02.076
I'm taking some shampoo
home like you told me to.

07:02.145 --> 07:03.664
And a few other things, so.
Okay, bye!

07:03.733 --> 07:05.942
- Um, okay. I never
got the chance to--

07:06.011 --> 07:07.668
thank you for all your help.

07:07.737 --> 07:10.222
Have a sunny day.

07:11.948 --> 07:15.814
- Lacey's Salon is open
for business!

07:15.883 --> 07:18.438
A sign to draw in
the customers!

07:18.507 --> 07:20.060
My tools of the trade.

07:20.129 --> 07:23.028
And a state of the art
salon chair.

07:23.097 --> 07:25.928
See? Just as cool
as Sunny's salon.

07:25.997 --> 07:29.725
Amazing what a car jack can do.
Going up!

07:29.794 --> 07:31.278
[jack rattling]

07:31.347 --> 07:32.900
- Whoa!

07:32.969 --> 07:38.147
Is it meant to be a
flying salon chair?

07:38.216 --> 07:40.874
Um, Lacey...

07:40.943 --> 07:44.049
Sunny's had lots of practice
styling hair.

07:44.118 --> 07:46.880
Maybe you should practice
a little too.

07:46.949 --> 07:47.846
- Practice?

07:47.915 --> 07:49.469
[laughing]

07:49.538 --> 07:52.195
Practice. Hmm...you may
have a point.

07:52.264 --> 07:54.232
I know! I'll practice on you!

07:54.301 --> 07:58.098
- Me? I didn't...I mean...

07:58.167 --> 07:59.513
My hair's not...

07:59.582 --> 08:01.998
You don't need practice!

08:02.067 --> 08:04.104
Whoa!

08:04.173 --> 08:06.831
Uh...

08:09.074 --> 08:11.870
- Let's do this.

08:11.939 --> 08:15.702
[humming]

08:15.771 --> 08:17.635
There! All finished!

08:17.704 --> 08:19.671
- No!

08:19.740 --> 08:22.536
- You're welcome.
I knew I was a natural.

08:22.605 --> 08:24.952
Now get up, we have
to pick up the Dame!

08:25.021 --> 08:26.885
Can't let Sunny
get there first.

08:26.954 --> 08:29.060
- Ugh.

08:33.167 --> 08:36.412
[bright music]

08:37.137 --> 08:40.899
- Oh, oops! Looks
like we missed a spot.

08:40.968 --> 08:42.211
- I got it! I got it!

08:42.280 --> 08:45.386
Make way for the towel
toboggan!

08:45.455 --> 08:46.698
Whoa!

08:46.767 --> 08:48.044
- Doodle!

08:48.113 --> 08:49.632
- Did I get it?

08:49.701 --> 08:51.013
- [giggles] Sure did, Doodle.

08:51.082 --> 08:53.222
[phone ringing]

08:53.291 --> 08:55.880
- Sunny's Salon.
Oh, hi, Timmy.

08:55.949 --> 08:57.019
Uh-huh.

08:57.088 --> 08:58.607
Great! I'll tell Sunny.

08:58.676 --> 09:01.782
Timmy says Dame Tralada
is done resting,

09:01.851 --> 09:03.473
and ready for her
styling.

09:03.543 --> 09:07.236
- Then we'd better pick her
♪ uh-uh-uh-up ♪

09:07.305 --> 09:08.237
[laughing]

09:08.306 --> 09:09.618
- Ready...

09:09.687 --> 09:10.998
Set...

09:11.067 --> 09:12.621
All: Gear up and go!

09:12.690 --> 09:15.624
[bright music]

09:15.693 --> 09:22.562
♪ ♪

09:22.631 --> 09:25.392
[engine revving]

09:25.461 --> 09:27.325
- Let me get the door for you,
Dame.

09:27.394 --> 09:29.707
- ♪ Thank you ♪

09:29.776 --> 09:32.606
- Oh.

09:32.675 --> 09:34.988
- ♪ Timothy ♪

09:35.057 --> 09:37.300
- Oof. Um...yes, Dame?

09:37.369 --> 09:40.752
- Hildegard's helmet. I shall
need it for the hairstylist.

09:40.821 --> 09:42.547
- Here you are, Dame.

09:42.616 --> 09:44.514
- Hi, Dame. We're here to take
you to get your hair done.

09:44.584 --> 09:46.931
- Hmm. You look familiar,

09:47.000 --> 09:50.728
but you're not the hairstylist
I met this morning.

09:50.797 --> 09:53.834
For one thing, she had a dog
and you have a--

09:53.903 --> 09:54.663
Oh my.

09:54.732 --> 09:57.148
What are you?

09:57.217 --> 09:58.667
- Not happy.

09:58.736 --> 10:01.946
- Yes, well, time
to do your hair.

10:02.015 --> 10:05.259
- Sunny sent you to pick
up the Dame, Lacey?

10:05.328 --> 10:09.091
That seems uh...
Not right.

10:09.160 --> 10:14.717
- Uh, well, I did help Sunny
earlier today. Right, KC?

10:14.786 --> 10:17.099
- She fixed her sink!
I was there.

10:17.168 --> 10:21.793
- Besides, Timmy, don't you
need to get some um...stuff?

10:21.862 --> 10:24.589
And do things for the Dame,
like now?

10:24.658 --> 10:26.902
- Ow!
- Oh, yes!

10:26.971 --> 10:30.560
Be a dear, Timothy and drop
off my costumes at the theater.

10:30.630 --> 10:32.045
I shall see you there.

10:32.114 --> 10:33.805
- Well, o-okay.

10:33.874 --> 10:36.981
I guess Lacey can take
you to get your hair done.

10:37.050 --> 10:38.603
- I'll take that.

10:38.672 --> 10:40.329
- ♪ Thank you, Timothy ♪

10:40.398 --> 10:42.262
- Whoa! Oh! Don't mention it.

10:42.331 --> 10:44.402
Oh, please.

10:44.471 --> 10:46.335
- Your ride, Ms. Dame!

10:46.404 --> 10:49.027
- Oh! Stylish!

10:49.096 --> 10:51.236
[engine whirrs]

10:51.305 --> 10:52.306
Hm.

10:52.375 --> 10:55.344
This is the Glam Van?

10:55.413 --> 10:59.313
Ugh. It is neither
glamorous nor a van!

10:59.382 --> 11:03.421
- It's my, um...Fabulou-cycle.

11:03.490 --> 11:05.665
Yeah, that's it. Hop in!

11:05.734 --> 11:06.666
- Oh.

11:06.735 --> 11:07.977
[engine revving]

11:08.046 --> 11:09.669
- Aah!

11:09.738 --> 11:10.946
[coughing]

11:11.015 --> 11:14.639
Ugh. I think I swallowed a bug!

11:14.708 --> 11:15.605
[engines roaring]

11:15.675 --> 11:19.540
[bright music]

11:19.609 --> 11:23.613
- [whistling]

11:23.683 --> 11:24.925
- Hi, Timmy!

11:24.994 --> 11:27.410
- Sunny? What are
you doing here?

11:27.479 --> 11:30.241
- We're here to pick up the
Dame, to do her hair!

11:30.310 --> 11:32.450
Is she ready for her
appointment?

11:32.519 --> 11:33.520
- The Dame?

11:33.589 --> 11:36.040
- Yep. You know, yea high,
and all

11:36.109 --> 11:38.076
♪ Timothy ♪

11:38.145 --> 11:39.871
- I know her.

11:39.940 --> 11:43.047
But it's just she already
left with Lacey.

11:43.116 --> 11:44.427
All: Lacey?

11:44.496 --> 11:46.119
- Wasn't she helping
you out today?

11:46.188 --> 11:48.466
- We didn't ask her
to pick up the Dame.

11:48.535 --> 11:50.019
All: Oh, boy.

11:50.088 --> 11:51.883
[chair creaks]

11:51.952 --> 11:53.782
- Dame Tra-la-la!

11:53.851 --> 11:55.300
- It's Tralada.

11:55.369 --> 11:57.026
- Whatever.

11:57.095 --> 12:01.479
So Dame Tralada, you are about
to get the best hairstyle ever!

12:01.548 --> 12:05.552
- Mm...and you're certain
Sunny sent you?

12:05.621 --> 12:08.175
- Look! I'm using her shampoo!

12:08.244 --> 12:12.559
See? Don't worry.
You're in good hands.

12:12.628 --> 12:14.388
- Hmm.

12:14.457 --> 12:15.700
- Let's see.

12:15.769 --> 12:17.633
♪ I'll snip a little here ♪

12:17.702 --> 12:19.324
♪ And clip a little there ♪

12:19.393 --> 12:21.913
♪ And flip a little over
to the side ♪

12:21.982 --> 12:23.432
- ♪ I just can't wait to see ♪

12:23.501 --> 12:24.744
- ♪ A dab of this shampoo ♪

12:24.813 --> 12:26.849
♪ And this I'll say to you ♪

12:26.918 --> 12:30.680
♪ Sunny would never think of
cutting hair the way we do ♪

12:30.750 --> 12:34.098
♪ At Lacey's Salon
Lacey's Salon ♪

12:34.167 --> 12:38.412
♪ For hairstyling skill
that you can count upon ♪

12:38.481 --> 12:39.793
♪ Hair's what I do ♪

12:39.862 --> 12:41.761
♪ It's the area I'm best in ♪

12:41.830 --> 12:43.590
- ♪ It looks a lot
like something ♪

12:43.659 --> 12:45.661
♪ that a bird would
build a nest in ♪

12:45.730 --> 12:48.457
together: ♪ Lacey's Salon
Lacey's Salon ♪

12:48.526 --> 12:50.148
- Oh boy.

12:50.217 --> 12:52.875
- ♪ Let all of your hairstyling
worries be gone ♪

12:52.944 --> 12:55.498
♪ Voila! It's time for me
to take a bow ♪

12:55.567 --> 12:56.879
- ♪ Can't wait to see my hair ♪

12:56.948 --> 12:58.501
- ♪ Yes, Sunny
would be amazed ♪

12:58.570 --> 13:00.020
- ♪ Oh yeah, she'd be amazed ♪

13:00.089 --> 13:02.160
- ♪ Yes, Sunny
would be amazed ♪

13:02.229 --> 13:06.130
together: ♪ If she could
see me now ♪

13:06.199 --> 13:07.959
- [screaming]

13:08.028 --> 13:09.098
- What was that?

13:09.167 --> 13:10.617
[screaming]

13:10.686 --> 13:15.277
- What did you do to my
beautiful hair?

13:15.346 --> 13:17.313
- But you look amazing!

13:17.382 --> 13:19.350
You just need to put
on your helmet!

13:19.419 --> 13:21.145
That'll tie the whole thing
together--

13:21.214 --> 13:23.975
- Oh no!

13:24.044 --> 13:25.252
- No!

13:25.321 --> 13:26.771
[all gasp]

13:26.840 --> 13:28.014
- Oopsie.

13:28.083 --> 13:31.603
- You've ruined my hair
and  my helmet?

13:31.672 --> 13:35.331
You are the worst
hairstylist ever!

13:35.400 --> 13:38.956
How can I perform in
"The Rinse Cycle" like this?

13:39.025 --> 13:40.336
- I could try to fix it.

13:40.405 --> 13:44.030
- ♪ No, no, no,
no opera tonight ♪

13:44.099 --> 13:45.963
The opera's cancelled.

13:46.032 --> 13:47.792
- Oh no!

13:52.383 --> 13:56.318
- Oh, why? Oh, not the helmet!

13:56.387 --> 13:58.044
- I'm so sorry!

13:58.113 --> 14:01.150
- Dame Tralada, why do you have
to cancel the opera?

14:01.219 --> 14:03.359
You can still sing, right?

14:03.428 --> 14:05.189
- It's not that simple, Rox.

14:05.258 --> 14:08.399
Dame Tralada has to look just
like Hildegard

14:08.468 --> 14:09.987
for "The Rinse Cycle."

14:10.056 --> 14:12.023
Two yellow braids and
a horned helmet.

14:12.092 --> 14:15.371
- And there is no time
to repair it!

14:15.440 --> 14:17.373
The performance starts soon!

14:17.442 --> 14:19.548
- We can't give up,
Dame Tralada!

14:19.617 --> 14:22.620
We'll fix your hair and get you
to the opera on time.

14:22.689 --> 14:27.763
- Well, I do hate to
disappoint my adoring fans.

14:27.832 --> 14:29.972
- We won't let you down.
Follow me!

14:30.041 --> 14:32.906
- Yeah, come on!

14:32.975 --> 14:38.947
- Now this is what
I call a Glam Van!

14:39.016 --> 14:42.882
- Don't feel so bad.
I like the Dame's hair.

14:42.951 --> 14:44.573
Sort of.

14:44.642 --> 14:46.816
If I didn't really look at it.

14:46.886 --> 14:48.404
- I just wanted everyone to see

14:48.473 --> 14:50.959
what a great hairstylist
I could be.

14:51.028 --> 14:53.202
And treat me like a rock star.

14:53.271 --> 14:56.447
But all I did was show them
that I'm not good at anything.

14:56.516 --> 14:58.483
- Oh.

14:58.552 --> 15:00.727
[engine revving]

15:00.796 --> 15:02.004
- Everything okay, Doodle?

15:02.073 --> 15:03.592
- Better than okay!

15:03.661 --> 15:05.421
While you fix her hair,
I'll get you there!

15:05.490 --> 15:07.596
Hey! That rhymes!

15:07.665 --> 15:09.425
- What about the Dame's helmet?

15:09.494 --> 15:11.048
It's broken!

15:11.117 --> 15:13.567
And she absolutely needs it to
play Hildegard!

15:13.636 --> 15:17.295
- I've got a plan! Rox, we'll
need hair extensions.

15:17.364 --> 15:18.848
Blair, you're with me.

15:18.918 --> 15:21.679
If Hildegard needs horns,
then we'll make some.

15:21.748 --> 15:23.819
- Yes, let's rock and roll!

15:23.888 --> 15:26.511
Or opera and roll!

15:26.580 --> 15:28.720
- Let's just get to work!

15:28.789 --> 15:31.309
- ♪ This is so exciting ♪

15:31.378 --> 15:33.898
- Let's start by washing that
green out of your hair.

15:33.967 --> 15:35.210
- Ooh!

15:35.279 --> 15:36.280
- Shampoo!

15:39.455 --> 15:40.698
Toner!

15:42.010 --> 15:42.942
Lemonade!

15:43.011 --> 15:44.150
- Lemonade?

15:44.219 --> 15:46.566
- This is thirsty work!

15:48.809 --> 15:52.020
Now for some encore-worthy
opera braids!

15:54.574 --> 15:59.820
- Uh-huh. A little purple,
a little pink.

15:59.889 --> 16:01.719
Ooh, yeah!

16:04.480 --> 16:06.310
- All shiny!

16:08.933 --> 16:09.969
- Now some twisting!

16:12.074 --> 16:15.008
[bright music]

16:15.077 --> 16:19.495
♪ ♪

16:19.564 --> 16:22.395
Add some super stick-um
hair gel.

16:26.606 --> 16:28.711
A little hairspray.

16:28.780 --> 16:30.058
Done!

16:30.127 --> 16:31.921
- New horns!
- Good idea, Sunny!

16:31.991 --> 16:33.889
- The finishing touch.

16:33.958 --> 16:36.098
Well, what do you think?

16:36.167 --> 16:37.582
[gasps]

16:37.651 --> 16:40.137
- Was that a good gasp,
or a bad gasp?

16:40.206 --> 16:41.793
- Wait for it.

16:41.862 --> 16:46.902
- [sings a scale]

16:46.971 --> 16:49.629
It is so original!

16:49.698 --> 16:52.701
Yet so Hildegard!

16:52.770 --> 16:57.395
- This is definitely one
for the Style Files.

16:57.464 --> 16:59.604
- The opera's about to start!

16:59.673 --> 17:01.330
We're going to be late!

17:01.399 --> 17:03.125
- Doodle, step on it!

17:03.194 --> 17:04.471
- You got it.

17:04.540 --> 17:05.990
[engine revs]

17:06.059 --> 17:11.444
[Dame Tralada practices
her scales]

17:11.513 --> 17:12.376
[loud bang]

17:12.445 --> 17:13.791
- Whoa!

17:13.860 --> 17:18.382
- A flat tire? You've got to be
kidding me!

17:18.451 --> 17:21.212
- It's only flat on the bottom;
the top's still round.

17:21.281 --> 17:22.524
That's good, right?

17:22.593 --> 17:24.974
- Not really.

17:25.044 --> 17:27.494
But the good news is,
we have a spare.

17:27.563 --> 17:31.050
The bad news is, I don't know
how to put it on.

17:31.119 --> 17:32.361
- Quick show of hands!

17:32.430 --> 17:35.226
Anybody know how to change
a flat tire?

17:35.295 --> 17:40.024
- ♪ Oh this is a tragedy ♪

17:40.093 --> 17:43.890
- Oh, now we'll never get
the Dame to the opera on time!

17:43.959 --> 17:45.754
- Never say never, Blair.

17:45.823 --> 17:48.170
- This is all Lacey's fault.

17:48.239 --> 17:52.899
- Lacey! That's it! You just
gave me a great idea, Rox!

17:52.968 --> 17:54.728
- Um...you're welcome?

17:54.797 --> 17:57.938
- Didn't KC say she changed
the tires on her motorcycle?

17:58.007 --> 18:00.769
She's sure to know how to
fix the tire on the Glam Van.

18:00.838 --> 18:03.841
- But wasn't it Lacey
who got us into this mess?

18:03.910 --> 18:06.947
- I think Lacey feels bad
about what she did.

18:07.016 --> 18:09.191
She deserves a chance to help.

18:09.260 --> 18:12.574
Hmm...Rox, can I borrow
your skateboard?

18:12.643 --> 18:13.644
- You got it!

18:13.713 --> 18:16.923
[bright music]

18:20.961 --> 18:22.791
[creaking]

18:22.860 --> 18:27.968
- Ugh, I still can't believe
I ruined the Dame's hair.

18:28.037 --> 18:30.350
Worst day ever!

18:30.419 --> 18:31.696
- Lacey!

18:31.765 --> 18:33.698
- It's Sunny! Quick, hide!

18:33.767 --> 18:37.288
- Uh...we're not here.

18:37.357 --> 18:38.565
- Huh?

18:38.634 --> 18:40.602
- She means she's here,
I'm not.

18:40.671 --> 18:43.156
- Lacey, please!
We need your help.

18:43.225 --> 18:46.642
- Why would you need my help?
I'm not good at anything.

18:46.711 --> 18:49.404
- Maybe hairstyling
isn't the thing for you,

18:49.473 --> 18:51.751
but everyone's good at
something, Lacey.

18:51.820 --> 18:53.649
- You think I'm good
at something?

18:53.718 --> 18:57.377
- Absolutely. Remember how you
fixed the sink

18:57.446 --> 18:58.930
in the salon today?

18:58.999 --> 19:00.346
- Anyone could do that.

19:00.415 --> 19:03.107
- Wrong. No one knew
how to do that.

19:03.176 --> 19:04.557
Except you!

19:04.626 --> 19:08.526
- Well, I guess I am a little
bit handy

19:08.595 --> 19:10.356
when it comes to
fixing things.

19:10.425 --> 19:11.495
- A little?

19:11.564 --> 19:14.049
She's the best fixer in town!

19:14.118 --> 19:15.602
- But how can I help?

19:15.671 --> 19:17.225
- We need you to help
change a flat tire.

19:17.294 --> 19:19.330
- Flat tire? Piece of cake.

19:19.399 --> 19:21.850
- To the Fabulou-Cycle!

19:21.919 --> 19:23.058
- The what?

19:23.127 --> 19:27.269
- The Fabulou-- Just come on.

19:27.338 --> 19:29.616
- We better not
forget the car jack.

19:29.685 --> 19:31.066
- I've got this.

19:31.135 --> 19:33.758
[bright music]

19:33.827 --> 19:35.967
[engine revving]

19:36.036 --> 19:39.833
- Mm. That should do it.

19:39.902 --> 19:42.146
- Lacey, you did it!

19:42.215 --> 19:44.666
- Yeah, you really know your
doodads

19:44.735 --> 19:46.392
from your other doodads!

19:46.461 --> 19:49.533
- Thanks! Oh,
just one more thing.

19:49.602 --> 19:50.982
Dame Tralada--

19:51.051 --> 19:53.744
- Ah! I am not letting
you do my makeup!

19:53.813 --> 19:55.470
- It's not that. It's just--

19:55.539 --> 20:00.337
Well, I'm sorry I ruined your
hair. I didn't mean to.

20:00.406 --> 20:02.684
And I'm sorry that
I picked up the Dame

20:02.753 --> 20:04.064
when I wasn't supposed to.

20:04.133 --> 20:06.964
- Thanks, Lacey.
Apology accepted.

20:07.033 --> 20:09.380
- As a token of my
appreciation,

20:09.449 --> 20:13.177
you are all invited
as my special guests

20:13.246 --> 20:14.937
to what's sure to be my

20:15.006 --> 20:20.219
♪ most spectacular
performance ever ♪

20:20.288 --> 20:23.808
- Really? I mean, sure,
I guess we could come.

20:23.877 --> 20:24.982
- Let's go!

20:25.051 --> 20:26.432
- Whoo-hoo!
- Yeah!

20:26.501 --> 20:28.434
[laughter]

20:28.503 --> 20:30.815
[engines revving]

20:30.884 --> 20:34.094
[bright music]

20:35.820 --> 20:37.857
- Why is everything so small?

20:40.308 --> 20:42.137
Yep, that's much better.

20:42.206 --> 20:44.622
- Hi, Sunny. Thanks for getting
the dame to the show on time.

20:44.691 --> 20:46.831
- Actually, that was all Lacey.

20:46.900 --> 20:49.938
Turns out, she's really great
at fixing things.

20:50.007 --> 20:51.388
- Well thanks, Lacey.

20:51.457 --> 20:54.839
- You're the best.

20:54.908 --> 20:57.428
[cheers and applause]

20:57.497 --> 20:59.637
- Oh, the Dame looks fantastic.

20:59.706 --> 21:01.398
- That was all Sunny.

21:01.467 --> 21:04.055
Turns out she really is the
best hairstylist in town.

21:04.124 --> 21:06.851
- Psst! Hey, KC!

21:06.920 --> 21:09.716
Come into the salon tomorrow
and I'll fix your hair!

21:09.785 --> 21:12.132
- Actually, it's sort
of growing on me.

21:12.201 --> 21:16.275
- Hooray! All right,
Dame Tralada!

21:16.344 --> 21:18.311
Ooh, I know her!

21:18.380 --> 21:23.109
[Sings Wagner's "Ride of the
Valkyries"]

21:23.178 --> 21:26.250
- She's a really good singer,
isn't she?

21:26.319 --> 21:28.183
- She's great,

21:28.252 --> 21:31.462
but you know, I bet
I could sing as good as her!

21:31.531 --> 21:33.257
- Here we go again!

21:33.326 --> 21:36.225
[laughter]

21:36.295 --> 21:39.539
[Tralada sings]

21:43.957 --> 21:45.234
- Hi, it's me, Sunny,

21:45.304 --> 21:47.547
with another look inside
the Style Files!

21:47.616 --> 21:49.860
I love those side braids!

21:49.929 --> 21:52.207
They look just like
Dame Tralada's!

21:52.276 --> 21:55.831
For this hairstyle and more,
check out Sunny's Style Files

21:55.900 --> 21:58.869
at nickjr.com
and The Nick Jr. app!

21:58.938 --> 22:02.321
Keep smiling, keep styling!
